## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Likely cause / fix |
|---|---|
| Tests interfere across runs | Check isolation; add cleanup in teardown |
| Async test times out | Raise the timeout, or confirm you awaited the call |
| Mock has no effect | Verify the mock path matches the import path |
| DB state leaks between tests | Check that the transaction rolls back |

